quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,85,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pé: "
  37,86,"Ṣé ẹ̀ ń gbèrò láti sọ irọ́ di ọlọ́hun lẹ́yìn Allāhu?"
  37,87,"Kí sì ni èrò ọkàn yín sí Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá?”{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, ẹ̀san rere ni ẹ̀ ń retí ni tàbí ẹ̀san aburú?]
  38,64,"Dájúdájú ìyẹn, àríyànjiyàn àwọn èrò inú Iná, òdodo mà ni."
  38,65,"Sọ pé: “Èmi ni olùkìlọ̀. Àti pé kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Allāhu, Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo, Olùborí."
  38,66,"Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà láààrin méjèèjì, Alágbára, Aláforíjìn.”"
  39,49,"Nígbà tí ìnira kan ba fọwọ́ ba ènìyàn, ó máa pè Wá. Lẹ́yìn náà, nígbà tí A bá fún un ní ìdẹ̀ra kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Wa, ó máa wí pé: “Wọ́n fún mi pẹ̀lú ìmọ̀ ni.”{1} Kò sì rí bẹ́ẹ̀, àdánwò ni, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀..",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, òun mọ̀ ọ́n ṣe ni tòun fi gún. Dípò kí ó moore sí Allāhu, kí ó dúpẹ́ fún Un, kí ó sì mọ̀ pé Allāhu fẹ́ bẹ́ẹ̀ fún un ni nínú kádàrá Rẹ̀ lórí rẹ̀.]
  39,50,"Àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn kúkú wí (irú) rẹ̀, ṣùgbọ́n ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ kò rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀."
  39,51,"Aburú ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ sì bá wọn. Àwọn alábòsí nínú àwọn wọ̀nyí náà, aburú ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ yóò bá wọn. Wọn kò sì níí mórí bọ́."
  40,28,"Ọkùnrin onígbàgbọ́ òdodo kan tó ń fi ìgbàgbọ́ rẹ̀ pamọ́ nínú àwọn ènìyàn Fir‘aon sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ máa pa ọkùnrin kan nítorí pé ó ń sọ pé, “Allāhu ni Olúwa mi.” Ó sì kúkú ti mú àwọn ẹ̀rí tó yanjú wá ba yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa yín. Tí ó bá jẹ́ òpùrọ́, (ìyà) irọ́ rẹ̀ wà lórí rẹ̀. Tí ó bá sì jẹ́ olódodo, apá kan èyí tí ó ṣe ní ìlérí fún yín yó sì kò le yín lórí. Dájúdájú Allāhu kò níí fi ọ̀nà mọ ẹni tí ó jẹ́ aláṣejù, òpùrọ́."
  40,29,"Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn mi, ẹ̀yin l’ẹ ni ìjọba lónìí, tí ẹ ga jùlọ lórí ilẹ̀ náà (ìyẹn ilẹ̀ Misrọ). Ṣùgbọ́n ta ni ó máa ràn wá lọ́wọ́ tí ìyà Allāhu bá dé bá wa?” Fir‘aon wí pé: “Èmi kò fi n̄ǹkan kan hàn yín bí kò ṣe ohun tí mo rí (nínú òye mi). Èmi kò sì tọ yín sí ọ̀nà kan bí kò ṣe ojú ọ̀nà ìmọ̀nà.”"
  40,30,"Ẹni tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo tún sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn mi, dájúdájú irú ọjọ́ (ẹ̀san ìyà tó ṣẹlẹ̀ sí) àwọn ọmọ-ogun oníjọ ni èmi ń páyà lórí yín;"
  41,7,"Àwọn tí kò yọ Zakāh, àwọn sì ni aláìgbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Bí āyah yìí bá sọpọ̀ mọ́ āyah tí ó ṣíwájú rẹ̀, “zakāh” máa dúró fún àfọ̀mọ́ ọkàn àti àfọ̀mọ́ ara. Àmọ́ tí āyah yìí bá dádúró, “zakāh” máa túmọ̀ sí àfọ̀mọ́ dúkìá.]
  41,8,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, ẹ̀san tí kò níí pẹ̀dín tí kò níí dáwọ́ dúró ń bẹ fún wọn."
  41,9,"Sọ pé: “Ṣé dájúdájú ẹ̀yin máa ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá ilẹ̀ fún ọjọ́ méjì, ẹ sì ń sọ (ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀) di akẹgbẹ́ Rẹ̀ (tí ẹ̀ ń bọ wọ́n)?” Ìyẹn (Ẹlẹ́dàá ilẹ̀) sì ni Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."